Class Measurements

    • Field Detail

      • results

        private List<List<Tuple>> results
        To make sure the results are really computed and the compiler doesn't skip anything, we keep a small subset (100) of the most recent results at all times. At the end of the computation print() adds the values of the tuples of the small result set and prints it.
